# ════════════════════════════════════════════════
# FILE: Gemfile
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# WHAT THIS DOES (plain language):
#   Lists the Ruby tool (fastlane) needed to build and upload the iOS app,
#   so CI can install an exact, repeatable version of it instead of
#   "whatever's newest today." Standard fastlane convention — pairs with
#   ios/fastlane/Fastfile and ios/fastlane/Appfile.
#
# NOTES / GOTCHAS:
#   - This alone does not require any Apple signing secrets — it is safe to
#     install/bundle at any time. The Fastfile lanes it enables are what's
#     inert until signing secrets exist (see ios/fastlane/Fastfile header).
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════

source "https://rubygems.org"

gem "fastlane"
